      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously preserved and mechanically superior, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a premier asset of investment-grade quality. Experience the pinnacle of automotive preservation.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
